      "review_summary": "The branch makes `MenuBarDisplayText.paceText` return `0%` when the rounded pace delta is zero and adds Swift Testing coverage for zero and signed non-zero pace labels.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source inspection: current main rounds `abs(deltaPercent)` and always prepends a sign, so sub-half-percent deltas can render as `+0%` or `-0%` through `MenuBarDisplayText.paceText`. I did not run tests because this review is read-only.",
